_sText:
THIS IS A REMAKE ! :-D
I was playing on a Jail server, when i saw this ugly map called ba_jail_electric_razor_v6 :cry:
My eyes started bleeding and my brain told me to do something, so.. ok braindo, I'll do a remake !
I'm not a naugthy boy, so I decided to share my work with all this lovely community <3

ABOUT THE MAP:
This map is similar to the original version, with a lot of new features, rescale and much more beautiful.

New games:

  • Playable football, with 2 styles ( Free, and matchmode -> Win system/3 goals for winning )
  • Simon says auto
  • Gun thrower
  • Russian roulette
  • Jumping rope
  • Random dice
  • Paper, rock, scissors
  • Private climbing for Last wish ( No entry, need plugins :cry: )
  • Private 1v1 room for Last wish ( No entry, need plugins :cry: )

New secrets teleport
There are some new teleports on the map, I let you find them.
